## 7\. ATUALIZAÇÃO DO DOCKER-COMPOSE (Monitoring Profile)

Adicione ao `docker-compose.yml` existente:

yamlCopy

 prometheus:  
    image: prom/prometheus:v2.51.0  
    container\_name: zehla-prometheus  
    restart: unless-stopped  
    command:  
      \- '--config.file=/etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml'  
      \- '--storage.tsdb.path=/prometheus'  
      \- '--storage.tsdb.retention.time=30d'  
      \- '--web.console.libraries=/usr/share/prometheus/console\_libraries'  
      \- '--web.console.templates=/usr/share/prometheus/consoles'  
      \- '--web.enable-lifecycle'  
    volumes:  
      \- ./prometheus/prometheus.yml:/etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml:ro  
      \- prometheus-data:/prometheus  
    networks:  
      \- zehla-internal  
    ports:  
      \- "127.0.0.1:9090:9090"  
    profiles:  
      \- monitoring

  *\# Exporters opcionais (descomente se necessário)*  
  *\# redis-exporter:*  
  *\#   image: oliver006/redis\_exporter:latest*  
  *\#   environment:*  
  *\#     REDIS\_ADDR: redis://redis:6379*  
  *\#     REDIS\_PASSWORD: ${REDIS\_PASSWORD}*  
  *\#   networks:*  
  *\#     \- zehla-internal*  
  *\#   profiles:*  
  *\#     \- monitoring*

  *\# postgres-exporter:*  
  *\#   image: prometheuscommunity/postgres-exporter:latest*  
  *\#   environment:*  
  *\#     DATA\_SOURCE\_NAME: postgresql://zehla:${POSTGRES\_PASSWORD}@postgres:5432/zehla?sslmode=disable*  
  *\#   networks:*  
  *\#     \- zehla-internal*  
  *\#   profiles:*

  *\#     \- monitoring*

